Class JavaDecafCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.JavaDecafCompiler

  • public class JavaDecafCompiler
extends java.lang.Object
    The main compiler class. Runs the precompiler on an input file then calls the system java compiler on it. Some code modified from JavaCC original parser code

      • precompile

        public java.lang.String precompile(java.io.File inputFile,
                                   java.io.PrintWriter ostr)
        Call the JavaCC parser on the file from args[0] to convert the JavaDecaf code to true Java. Use the name of the JDC file for the name of the Java class, and check its validity as a Java classname.
        Parameters:
        inputFile - the file to be used as input, to become Java class name
        ostr - the PrintWriter to print to (file or console)
        Returns:
        the filename of the converted java file, null if something goes wrong
